These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
City: hamburg, nizza
2 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| City   | nizza  | hamburg |
| Pet       | snake | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, pear
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, siglo
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
2. the person eating pear is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Food   | peach | pear |
| Cigar      | siglo     | baccarat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, blue
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee  |
| Color   | pink | blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, black
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, bus
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Color   | black | yellow   |
| Transport       | bus | train |

